Globalization impact on tourism. Competitiveness. External competitiveness forces (and internal competitiveness forces).Objectives/eesmärkid:  The goal of this course is to provide comprehensive knowledge on external competitiveness forces (trends and threats) and internal competitiveness forces (strengths and weaknesses).Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) understands factors influencing competitiveness in domestic and international markets; 2) understands clusters and collaboration networks, and knows how to build and manage strategic partnerships; 3) develops strategies for tourism entrepreneurship and destinations to increase competitiveness, as well as tactics of companies.
